{"title":"心愿","authors":["光军"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉门矿务局　光军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏祁连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒令戈壁："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把黑金贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是勘探队员的雄心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是地质工作者的誓言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们会遇到困难阻挡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们的决心决不改变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野外战斗的日日夜夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁滩上的千难万险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没拦住我们前进的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开出油田的心愿丝毫不减。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有党的亲切教导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有毛主席的谆谆指点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们方向明确，永远向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国奋斗，前途无限。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《石油工人报》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}